txt.en: You collected meat and hides from the crocodiles along the shore. Return them to Tevurin at the hunter's expedition camp in southeastern Cape of Umbar.
Demand remains high for the trappings obtained by hunting crocodiles. Go to the shore west of the expedition camp, hunt the crocodiles for their hides and meat.
'Head to the west along the shore and hunt the crocodiles there for their hides and their meat. Return both to me here at the camp when you are done.'
'Head to the west along the shore and hunt the crocodiles there for their hides and their meat. Return both to me here at the camp when you are done.'
Return the hides and meat to Tevurin at the expedition camp

The demand for crocodile hides and meat persists. Tevurin dispatched you back to the beach west of the expedition camp to collect enough of the hides and meat to meet the demand of the citizens in Umbar.

'The demand for crocodile meat and hides remain high, friend. The latest requests want enough hides and meat to sustain my patron for a week. Go west to the shore, hunt the crocodiles for the meat and hides, and return to me when you've finished your collection.'
Return the hides and meat to Tevurin at the expedition camp

'I do not think the demand for the hides and meat of the crocodiles will ever diminish. I only see the demand growing as more citizens realize the value of the hide. The meat is an acquired taste. It seems that more and more are acquiring it daily.\n\n'Thank you for your continued effort, [placeholder].'
